data.description:
Have you ever dreamed of owning a spacious, two-story home on a vast, country property? Well, look no further, this is the dream home you've been searching for.

As you drive up to the property, you'll be greeted by a beautifully landscaped lawn with various flowers, shrubs, and a fruit tree in the front yard that add charm and character to the home. 

This country dream is a five-bedroom, three-bathroom house situated on two acres. 
Entering the home, you'll be immediately greeted by the warmth and inviting atmosphere of the living room that features large windows that let in natural light and offer a spectacular view of the picturesque surroundings of the property. It also possesses a wood burning fireplace that adds ambiance and an alternate source of heat for those winter nights.

The kitchen which is the heart of the house comes equipped with all the modern amenities that you'll need. You'll love the sleek look of the stainless steel appliances, built in wine fridge and granite countertops. 

The spacious primary bedroom is downstairs. Across the living room you will find a hallway with 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The 4th bedroom is at the top of the stairs and shares a full Jack and Jill bathroom with the 5th oversized bedroom. The 5th bedroom could be used as a second primary bedroom, perfect in-law sweet or entertainment room; the options are endless when it comes to this room!

The freshly painted deck with a covered patio is the perfect place to spend quality time outdoors with family and friends.

There is ample amount of parking space for your vehicles in the 2 car garage and driveway. The property is also equipped with 2 storage sheds.

So come get a taste of country living!
